data.description: Seller wants QUICK CLOSING!One of the largest single family homes in convenient  South Middle River area of Fort Lauderdale that offers 4 bedrooms 2 full baths with over 2000 sf on an interior fenced lot. Huge living room, dining room and a seperate great room with a 3 way split bedroom layout for privacy plus a large interior laundry room. No carpet! Smooth ceilings and 6 panel doors! Large covered patio and a sun deck plus a shed. Newer appliances including a French door SS refrigerator and an extra refrigerator. Primary bedroom is an ensuite with updated white cabinet and stone surface. Close to downtown, highways , beaches, Las Olas, Wilton Manors, restaurants and shopping. Great for investors for a rental or Airbnb. Plenty of room to entertain and large driveway. Tons of potential!
